seatuya
=======

A C wrapper library for tuyapp, providing a pure C API for Tuya
smart-device communication.

Building
--------

    autoreconf -fi
    ./configure
    make
    make check
    make install

Dependencies
------------

- tuyapp (C++ Tuya library)
- A C99 compiler
- A C++ compiler (for linking against tuyapp)
- GNU autotools (autoconf, automake, libtool) for building from git

